sequenceDiagram
    participant User as External Client
    participant Ingress as Ingress Controller<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Service as Llama Stack Service<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Pod as Llama Stack Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Backend as Inference Provider<br/>(Ollama/vLLM/TGI)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as Operator Manager<br/>ServiceAccount JWT
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Bearer Token Auth

    Note over User,Backend: Flow 1: User Inference Request (with Ingress)
    User->>Ingress: POST /v1/inference<br/>Auth: Optional (app-level)
    Ingress->>Service: Forward to ClusterIP<br/>HTTP (internal)
    Service->>Pod: Route to Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    Pod->>Backend: Inference Request<br/>HTTP/gRPC (varies)
    Backend-->>Pod: Inference Response
    Pod-->>Service: JSON Response
    Service-->>Ingress: Response
    Ingress-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over User,Operator: Flow 2: LlamaStackDistribution Reconciliation
    User->>K8sAPI: Create LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event notification<br/>ServiceAccount JWT
    Operator->>Operator: Generate manifests<br/>kustomize templates
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply Deployment/Service/PVC/NetworkPolicy<br/>ServiceAccount JWT
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources created

    Note over Prom,Operator: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
    Prom->>Proxy: GET /metrics<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    Proxy->>Proxy: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview
    Proxy->>Operator: Forward to localhost:8080<br/>HTTP (no auth)
    Operator-->>Proxy: Prometheus metrics
    Proxy-->>Prom: Metrics (HTTPS)

    Note over User,Operator: Flow 4: ConfigMap-driven Configuration Update
    User->>K8sAPI: Update ConfigMap<br/>(feature flags or image overrides)
    K8sAPI->>Operator: ConfigMap watch event<br/>ServiceAccount JWT
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Reconcile affected LlamaStackDistributions<br/>ServiceAccount JWT
    K8sAPI->>Pod: Restart pods with new config
